```

**`/home/aditya/projects/alpauls-ats/src/rpc/router/client.ts`** — file upload key:
```ts
// line 117
const key = `clients/${crypto.randomUUID()}/${input.filename}`;
```

### D. better-auth internal ID generation

better-auth itself generates UUIDs internally for its own operations (sessions, verification tokens, etc.) — the library handles this automatically. The config in `/home/aditya/projects/alpauls-ats/src/lib/auth/server.ts` does not override any ID generation; it uses the default.

### E. No other ID libraries found

**No** usage of `nanoid`, `uuid` (the npm package), `generateId`, or `createId` was found anywhere in `src/`.

